abstract: >-
  SoulSketch is an open protocol and reference implementation for capturing
  an AI assistant's "memory pack" - persona, relationships, technical context,
  voice, and runtime observations - in a portable, version-controlled format
  that can be carried across model upgrades, platforms, and machines.
